<L>__{exterior otisville f.c.i. new york 1999 day}
<A>__{george pushes dirt along the edge of a flower root. still planting those sunflowers, he presses down firmly, standing before him is barbara, still beautiful and young with flowing locks. george raises his hand and makes a small wave. barbara opens and closes her hand. bye bye.}
